r-rute-yogya-makassar-hilang-kontak-di-maros'>An Indonesia Air Transport ATR 42-512 aircraft operated by the marine affairs ministry carrying eleven people loses contact in Maros Regency, South Sulawesi, while flying to Makassar and crashes. A search and rescue effort is underway. (Detikcom in Indonesian)</a> - detik.com</li></ul>